11/25/2024,748.2151(c)(6) - Medication,Medication,No,12/06/2024,12/16/2024,L:Medication,Medium,Yes,"Medication logs include the signature and a cell for staff initials. The documentation doesn't include the name of the person who administered the medication, and several dates doesn't have an initial to match the person who administered the medication.","On December 16, 2024, Inspector conducted a follow-up inspection at the operation and reviewed all medication logs with the staff.  All medication logs were observed to include the staff name, staff signature, and staff initials for each staff member who administered the medication."
