11/25/2024,748.2151(d) - Medication,Medication,No,12/06/2024,12/16/2024,L:Medication,Medium High,Yes,All medication logs had an inaccurate daily count due to incorrect subtraction from the starting count.,"On December 16, 2024, Inspector conducted a follow-up inspection at the operation and reviewed all medication logs and counted the medication with the staff.  One medication log and the medication were observed to have inaccurate counts.  Operation provided documentation that the child refused the medication including additional attempt of refusal, and the medication log was corrected during the inspection to document the refusal, and the count was updated to reflect the accurate remaining count. "
06/06/2024,748.363(7) - Reports and Record Keeping,Reports and Record Keeping,No,06/20/2024,06/10/2024,D:Reports and Record Keeping,Medium,Yes,Active employee file didn't include a notarized affidavit..,"The following compliance plan was provided by the operation on Saturday, June 8, 2024: A Notarized affidavit was emailed to Residential Child Care Licensing Inspector on 06/06/2024. The affidavit was completed on 06/06/2024. All staff who apply for a position at Amazing Touch Care Home will be required to get the affidavit notarized during the initial application process. The Program Administrator and Program Director will ensure the affidavit is notarized before we move forward with the hiring process which includes submitting the background check and pre-service orientation."
06/06/2024,748.3019(b) - Safety and Emergency Practices,Safety and Emergency Practices,No,06/20/2024,06/10/2024,O:Safety and Emergency Practices,Medium,Yes,The second level of the home was observed with wasps nests outside of the home. ,"The following compliance plan was provided by the operation on Saturday, June 8, 2024: Photographs of the wasp nests removal were emailed to the Residential Child Care Licensing Inspector on 06/06/2024. The wasp nest was removed on 06/06/2024. The Program Administrator, Program Director, and Maintenance supervisor will complete a daily facility inspection at Amazing Touch Care Home of the interior and exterior to ensure compliance. The facility inspection forms will be kept in a binder located in the staff office and available upon request."
